question: Nai kong-tiong teh koat-chhut ê tsu-liāu tiong, ū sím-mih kang-huē tit-tioh tsuè koân ê phò-hun-tiám tsìn-ka, jî-tóo kî-tiong ê phò-hun-tiam sī sím-mih, jî-tóo i ê tsiáh sī sím-mih?
Ū-kúi ê chheh liat-toaⁿ ê chheh ū chhut-pán nî-tāi kah 'a' ê im, sī hōe piáu-sī te̍k-tēng ê pán-pún ia̍h-sī hōe-gī phài-tōaⁿ?
“Tōa-chū kiàⁿ-chòe-chiàⁿ ê LLM khut-hng” ê gián-kiù teh sú-iōng siáⁿ-chóng ê hong-hoat?
Tī té-sì o̍h-chha̍h ê si̍t-chè sî-kan tòe siáⁿ oa̍h-chok lâi jīn-chèng i ê kiat-kó?

Chiah-sī ài siá chhut toh-ê kang-lōe, i ê hong-hoat-lūn ū ēng siang-chân ki-chè (dual-mechanism) á-sī koàn-chân (hierarchical) ê hong-sek lâi chòe, chiah-ê kang-lōe teh thê-chhut ê tiōng-iàu sîn-sin sī sím-mih?
answer: Heterogeneous graph learning from earnings calls data

question: Tī lia̍t chhut ê chok-phín tiong, ū kúi-choá ê bīn-tō͘ bêng-khak tùi 'attention' chòe in ki-báⁿ chhòng-sin ê chi̍t-pō͘-hun?
Nāi LARA hù-kò͘-chè ê hoat-tiân tì-sū ki-jīn ê phín-sū-tō͘ siōng-ka 10% kā boán-chū ê ki-jíⁿ tō͘, sin ê phín-sū-tō͘ ē sī siáⁿ-mih?

Àm-chhiūⁿ chòe tâi, chhin-chhiūⁿ ki-su̍t hong-hoat ê tiāu-kiāⁿ (pí-lû, chhú-lí koan-hē ê tìn-tō hām chu-liāu cheng-ka) hām i só͘ pò-kò ê kiat-kó ê hâm-kòai (pí-lû, chē-chē chhī-tiâⁿ ê cheng-siong hām jîn-hô ê kái-piàn) ū siáⁿ-mi̍h koan-hē? Che ē-tàng tùi chhit-tâi lâi khoàⁿ chhut--lâi bô?
answer: Àm-chhiūⁿ ki-su̍t hong-hoat ê tiāu-kiāⁿ hām i só͘ pò-kò ê kiat-kó ê hâm-kòai ū chi̍t-ê koan-liân. Chhiūⁿ, MGDPR, i ê hong-hoat tiāⁿ chòe 'Sûn-tōng koan-hē chhú-lí', pò-kò chē-chē tōa-chām chhī-tiâⁿ (NASDAQ, NYSE, Shanghai) ê cheng-siong. Tò-o̍h, SH-Mix, i ê hong-hoat tiāⁿ chòe chi̍t-ê koh-khah cheng-tē ê ki-su̍t hong-hoat ('Pēⁿ-chàn ê phó͘-chè cheng-ka'), pò-kò i ê kiat-kó chòe 'chē-chē jîn-hô ê kái-piàn', chha-put-to sī kóng i ê éng-hiáng koh-khah chē-chē, sī koan-hē lâi ê jîn-hô ê éng-hiáng, bô ti̍t-chiap ê chhī-tiâⁿ tiâu-khòng.

question: 2024 nî ê chok-phín tiong, ūi-hē ê bó-chām chòe hù-hō-lē, ū hun-pia̍t ê phòe-tāi sêng-tióng, bô-tāi-khu-sè ê pí-tē, chāi-liāu ê kài-su̍t, kap kim-hiông ê tiâu-liám, che sī `Primary Results` ê bó-chām?

Chiu chiah kong-choe ê kiat-kwo sī sǹg-chòe chi̍t ê îⁿ-gōa-chha̍t, in-ūi i sī iōng chi̍t ê tùi hū kài-tōaⁿ ê tùi hū ê tùi hū chha̍t-tōaⁿ lâi piáu-sī, chi̍t ê tan-it ê tiám-sò͘ he̍k chi̍t ê thàⁿ-liâm ê biâu-siâu lâi piáu-sī bô-khó-lîm.
ECHO-GL Liu et al. ê kong-lāi pí goân-lâi ê model siâⁿ pháiⁿ kúi-jī?
answer: It improved prediction accuracy (F1) by 2.297% and correlation with actual market trends (MCC) by 15.629%, indicating better overall prediction performance.
